tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE inventory_updates (
 update_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 product_id INT,
 update_time TIMESTAMP,
 update_quantity INT,
 FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Inventory (
    inventory_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    stock INT,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES Product(product_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Order (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    order_date TIMESTAMP,
    status VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES Product(product_id)
);
CREATE TABLE inventory (id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_name STRING, quantity INT, price DECIMAL);
CREATE TABLE orders (order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_id INT, quantity INT, order_date TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE customers (customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, customer_name STRING, email STRING, phone_number STRING);
CREATE TABLE sales (sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY, order_id INT, product_id INT, sale_date TIMESTAMP);
